 We also need a soldering iron. 

00:01:05.180 --> 00:01:07.460
 Well, let's get started! 

00:01:07.460 --> 00:01:10.120
 First you need to remove the battery cover, 

00:01:10.120 --> 00:01:12.360
 since there are two screws under it. 

00:01:12.540 --> 00:01:13.500
 Here 

00:01:14.100 --> 00:01:14.840
